ZH: 你真是个蠢蛋!
EN: You are such a idiot!

ZH: 不要再骗我了，你这个蠢蛋！
EN: Stop lying to me, you foolish idiot!

ZH: 他开车竟然违规停车，真是个蠢蛋。
EN: He parked illegally while driving, what a moron.

ZH: 我不愿意和那个蠢蛋交朋友。
EN: I don't want to be friends with that idiot.

ZH: 她把车钥匙丢在办公室，真是个蠢蛋。
EN: She left her car keys in the office, what an idiot.

ZH: 每次他都迟到，真是个蠢蛋。
EN: He's always late, such a fool.

ZH: 你为什么要相信他说的话？你就是个蠢蛋。
EN: Why did you believe what he said? You're just a stupid idiot.

ZH: 他没能及时完成任务，真是个大蠢蛋。
EN: He failed to complete the task on time, what a big idiot.

ZH: 别再做蠢事了，你这个蠢蛋！
EN: Stop doing stupid things, you idiot!

ZH: 你千万别再犯蠢了，蠢蛋！
EN: Don't make any more stupid mistakes, you idiot!

ZH: 他竟然忘了带钱包，真是个蠢蛋。
EN: He actually forgot his wallet, what an idiot.

ZH: 你为什么老是犯这样的错误？你真是个蠢蛋。
EN: Why do you keep making such mistakes? You are such a fool.

ZH: 别再跟他争论了，他就是个蠢蛋。
EN: Stop arguing with him, he's just a idiot.

ZH: 不要低估那个蠢蛋，他可能会给你带来麻烦。
EN: Don't underestimate that idiot, he may cause you trouble.

ZH: 他连个简单的问题都解答不出来，真是个蠢蛋。
EN: He couldn't even answer a simple question, what a moron.

ZH: 这么简单的任务你都做不好，你真是个蠢蛋。
EN: You can't even complete such a simple task, you foolish idiot.

ZH: 他竟然把自己的手机放进洗衣机里，真是个蠢蛋。
EN: He actually put his phone in the washing machine, what a idiot.

ZH: 你不该相信他的谎言，你是个蠢蛋。
EN: You shouldn't have believed his lies, you're an idiot.

ZH: 他就是个蠢蛋，把自己的工作坏了。
EN: He's just a idiot, he ruined his own work.

ZH: 你真是个蠢蛋，怎么就不明白我的意思呢？
EN: You're such an idiot, how can't you understand what I mean?

ZH: 别再做无谓的争吵了，你是个蠢蛋。
EN: Stop arguing for no reason, you're an idiot.
